ot wanting to stay in shelters. You have to be there at 3:30pm, get up and out by 6am, no privacy, stuff gets stolen and lots of problems keeping your meds safe. On the other hand, and this will probably be seen as judgmental, they wouldn&amp;#39;t make those signs if there were no reason to do so.</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/109915381192378495/comments/default/5394908960464685860'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/109915381192378495/comments/default/5394908960464685860'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2004/10/shelters-are-for-someone-else-part-2.html?showComment=1282033949971#c5394908960464685860' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2004/10/shelters-are-for-someone-else-part-2.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-109915381192378495' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/posts/default/109915381192378495' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1249668128"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="1:32 AM"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-1964493727655853111</id><published>2010-06-19T10:01:02.062-07:00</published><updated>2010-06-19T10:01:02.062-07:00</updated><title type='text'>Eloquent comments, NAB. Thank you for that.</title><content type='html'>Eloquent comments, NAB. Thank you for that.</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/109915381192378495/comments/default/1964493727655853111'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/